title: NYC High Line-Area Building Floats $53 Million Bankruptcy Sale
description: A commercial loft housing art galleries and photographers’ studios in West Chelsea has filed for bankruptcy to halt foreclosure by its lender, JPMorgan Chase & Co., as it seeks to close a $53 million deal to sell the property.
